class components - receives props as i/p and gives o/p as html(JSX). class component maintain krta h info.(state) jo private h 

2 types of components
function components - are simple functions that recive props and return a declaration. try to use functional components only all the time.
this keyword use krne kii zarurat nhi hogi q ki wo confusiong hoga, this functional me nhi chlta
yaha pe state nhi h components k jo confuse krte h 
functional comp me logics complex nhi hote bas UI k liye hi hota h 


class components - 
featrue jyada dete h, complex UI logic likh kste h , khudka private data(state) maintain kr skte h ,
provides lifecycle hooks
isko stateful/smart/container components b bolte h 

